Data Binding? 

 With the new annotation @XBAutoBind, collections and values may be modified without declaring
 getters and setters.

----------------------------------------
<xml>
   <list>
      <entry>foo</entry>
      <entry>bar</entry>
      <entry>something</entry>
   </list>
</xml>
----------------------------------------

